{"article_id":"VIyQelY9mDrIfPL3","edus":[{"id":0,"text":"President Trump on Monday accused Deputy Attorney General Rod Rosenstein and former FBI Deputy Director Andrew McCabe of pursuing an \" illegal and treasonous \" plot against him ,","depth":4},{"id":1,"text":"after McCabe detailed private DOJ discussions","depth":5},{"id":2,"text":"about secretly recording and potentially ousting the president .","depth":5},{"id":3,"text":"The alleged discussions have been a subject of fierce debate","depth":5},{"id":4,"text":"- and conflicting accounts -","depth":5},{"id":5,"text":"for months .","depth":4},{"id":6,"text":"But McCabe revived the issue during promotional interviews for his forthcoming book ,","depth":3},{"id":7,"text":"telling CBS News ' `` 60 Minutes ''","depth":4},{"id":8,"text":"that Rosenstein was \" absolutely serious \"","depth":5},{"id":9,"text":"when he suggested recording Trump in the tumultuous days","depth":6},{"id":10,"text":"following James Comey 's firing as FBI director .","depth":6},{"id":11,"text":"FORMER TOP FBI LAWYER :","depth":4},{"id":12,"text":"TWO TRUMP CABINET OFFICIALS WERE 'READY TO SUPPORT ' 25TH AMENDMENT EFFORT","depth":4},{"id":13,"text":"Trump seethed on Twitter over the comments ,","depth":7},{"id":14,"text":"calling McCabe a liar","depth":7},{"id":15,"text":"before lashing out at top DOJ and FBI officials ,","depth":8},{"id":16,"text":"including ousted Attorney General Jeff Sessions ,","depth":8},{"id":17,"text":"for what he described as a \" deranged \" plan .","depth":7},{"id":18,"text":"\" He and Rod Rosenstein ,","depth":10},{"id":19,"text":"who was hired by Jeff Sessions","depth":11},{"id":20,"text":"( another beauty ) ,","depth":11},{"id":21,"text":"look like they were planning a very illegal act ,","depth":9},{"id":22,"text":"and got caught ...","depth":8},{"id":23,"text":"There is a lot of explaining to do to the millions of people","depth":8},{"id":24,"text":"who had just elected a president","depth":9},{"id":25,"text":"who they really like","depth":10},{"id":26,"text":"and who has done a great job for them with the Military , Vets , Economy and so much more .","depth":10},{"id":27,"text":"This was the illegal and treasonous ' insurance policy ' in full action ! \"","depth":7},{"id":28,"text":"he tweeted .","depth":8},{"id":29,"text":"\" Insurance policy \" is a reference to texts between former FBI officials Peter Strzok and Lisa Page","depth":11},{"id":30,"text":"discussing such a policy ,","depth":11},{"id":31,"text":"without elaborating","depth":10},{"id":32,"text":"- the text was widely suspected of referring to aspects of the Russia collusion probe .","depth":9},{"id":33,"text":"While Trump fumed at McCabe ,","depth":7},{"id":34,"text":"the former FBI deputy director claimed","depth":8},{"id":35,"text":"he `` never actually considered taking [ Rosenstein ] up on the offer . ''","depth":8},{"id":36,"text":"He said","depth":8},{"id":37,"text":"he did discuss the matter with the FBI 's then-general counsel , James A. Baker .","depth":8},{"id":38,"text":"Last fall ,","depth":10},{"id":39,"text":"as reported by Fox News ,","depth":12},{"id":40,"text":"Baker told lawmakers during a closed-door deposition","depth":12},{"id":41,"text":"that McCabe and Page came to Baker `` contemporaneously ''","depth":12},{"id":42,"text":"and told him details of the meeting","depth":13},{"id":43,"text":"where Rosenstein made the comments .","depth":13},{"id":44,"text":"Baker told congressional investigators","depth":10},{"id":45,"text":"he took the word of McCabe and Page `` seriously . ''","depth":10},{"id":46,"text":"McCabe told CBS News","depth":11},{"id":47,"text":"that","depth":11},{"id":48,"text":"`` I think","depth":12},{"id":49,"text":"the general counsel had a heart attack ''","depth":12},{"id":50,"text":"when he told him of Rosenstein 's plan .","depth":11},{"id":51,"text":"`` And","depth":11},{"id":52,"text":"when he got up off the floor ,","depth":12},{"id":53,"text":"he said ,","depth":13},{"id":54,"text":"' I , I , that 's a bridge too far .","depth":14},{"id":55,"text":"We 're not there yet , ' ''","depth":14},{"id":56,"text":"McCabe added .","depth":10},{"id":57,"text":"Days later , Rosenstein appointed former FBI Director Robert Mueller as a special counsel","depth":6},{"id":58,"text":"to oversee the bureau 's investigation into allegations of collusion between the Trump campaign and Russian officials .","depth":6},{"id":59,"text":"Rosenstein repeatedly has denied","depth":6},{"id":60,"text":"he `` pursued or authorized recording the president ''","depth":6},{"id":61,"text":"and also has denied McCabe 's suggestion","depth":6},{"id":62,"text":"that the deputy attorney general had broached the idea","depth":7},{"id":63,"text":"of invoking the Constitution 's 25th Amendment ,","depth":8},{"id":64,"text":"which allows Cabinet members to seek the removal of a president","depth":9},{"id":65,"text":"if they conclude","depth":10},{"id":66,"text":"that he or she is mentally unfit .","depth":10},{"id":67,"text":"The Justice Department echoed both denials in a statement","depth":7},{"id":68,"text":"released last week ,","depth":7},{"id":69,"text":"saying","depth":7},{"id":70,"text":"Rosenstein `` was not in a position","depth":8},{"id":71,"text":"to consider invoking the 25th Amendment . ''","depth":8},{"id":72,"text":"Yet McCabe said in the interview ,","depth":7},{"id":73,"text":"`` Rod raised the [ 25th Amendment ] issue","depth":8},{"id":74,"text":"and discussed it with me in the context","depth":9},{"id":75,"text":"of thinking about how many other Cabinet officials might support such an effort. \"","depth":9},{"id":76,"text":"He added","depth":7},{"id":77,"text":"that he believed","depth":8},{"id":78,"text":"Rosenstein was `` counting votes or possible votes ''","depth":9},{"id":79,"text":"to remove Trump from office .","depth":9},{"id":80,"text":"Fox News reported Sunday","depth":6},{"id":81,"text":"that Baker , in his testimony to Congress , provided even more details about the alleged 25th Amendment discussions","depth":6},{"id":82,"text":"- saying","depth":6},{"id":83,"text":"two Cabinet officials were \" ready to support \" such an effort .","depth":6},{"id":84,"text":"\" I was being told by some combination of Andy McCabe and Lisa Page , that , in a conversation with the Deputy Attorney General , he had stated","depth":6},{"id":85,"text":"that he","depth":8},{"id":86,"text":"-- this was what was related to me --","depth":8},{"id":87,"text":"that he had at least two members of the president ' s Cabinet","depth":8},{"id":88,"text":"who were ready to support ,","depth":9},{"id":89,"text":"I guess","depth":11},{"id":90,"text":"you would call it ,","depth":11},{"id":91,"text":"an action under the 25th Amendment , \"","depth":10},{"id":92,"text":"Baker testified .","depth":5}],"relations":[{"parent":185,"left":103,"right":184,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":103,"left":98,"right":102,"relation":"context","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":98,"left":95,"right":97,"relation":"context","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":95,"left":0,"right":94,"relation":"context","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":94,"left":1,"right":2,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":97,"left":96,"right":5,"relation":"same-unit","nuclearity":"NN"},{"parent":96,"left":3,"right":4,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":102,"left":6,"right":101,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":101,"left":7,"right":100,"relation":"attribution","nuclearity":"SN"},{"parent":100,"left":8,"right":99,"relation":"context","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":99,"left":9,"right":10,"relation":"context","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":184,"left":150,"right":183,"relation":"joint","nuclearity":"NN"},{"parent":150,"left":104,"right":149,"relation":"organization","nuclearity":"SN"},{"parent":104,"left":11,"right":12,"relation":"attribution","nuclearity":"SN"},{"parent":149,"left":123,"right":148,"relation":"elaboration","nucl